item.title: CVE-2023-5131|2024-08-02T07:44:54.015Z -- delta%20electronics -- ispsoft
item.description: A heap buffer-overflow exists in Delta Electronics ISPSoft. An anonymous attacker can exploit this vulnerability by enticing a user to open a specially crafted DVP file to achieve code execution.
